{"title":"仓储","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1623","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>仓库里有三种货物，重量为<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1</span><span style=\"\">、</span>2、<span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3</span><span style=\"\">吨。现在要将货物堆成Ｐ堆，堆放规则如下：任意两堆的重量差不得超过３吨；在同一堆中，任意上下两个货物必须满足上面货物的重量不超过下面的货物。请写一程序来堆放这些货物。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行为整数Ｎ，表示共有Ｎ个货物(2≤N≤1000)<span style=\"\">；</span>第二行为整数Ｐ，表示要堆成Ｐ堆(1≤P，P*2≤N)；第三行有Ｎ个整数，表示每个货物的重量，中间用空格分隔。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p0\">输出文件有Ｐ行，每行描述一堆货物。描述格式为：从下到上列出该堆中每个货物的重量。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6</p>\n<p>3</p>\n<p>3 2 2 1 1 1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<div>\n<p>3 1</p>\n<p>2 1</p>\n<p>2 1</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}